name: DinnerDecider
0:
”Alexa, ask Dinner Decider to tell me what is for dinner.”
”Alexa, ask Dinner Decider to tell me what I should order.”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dinner decider
des: This unique skill will give you a random type of food that you can order for dinner if you need help deciding. Just ask!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
